 1055, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I won a gold at Euro skills in Gdansk, but now I am going to find out how good I am against the very best in the World.\\\"\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"score\": 0.999930269892225, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gdansk\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"Euro skills\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"the World\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old gained a first-class degree in architectural technology at Sheffield Hallam University and now works for professional services consulting firm WSP, handling majorbusinessprojects.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.969290401026914e-22, \"text\": \"Sheffield Hallam\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\", \"score\": 0.9951493713216759, \"rank\": 0.004874271632372265, \"text\": \"WSP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a first-class degree\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"architectural technology\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"professional services\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"majorbusinessprojects\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was while she was studying that she heard about the competition through one of her lecturers who suggested she should take part.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"her lecturers\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But winning is not the main objective for Isabelle who is focused on enjoying the environment and scale of the competition while also connecting with like-minded people.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main objective\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"Isabelle\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"scale\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"like-minded people\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I do not think I am prepared for the scale of the competition and what it will be like, it will just be immense.\\\"\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scale\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year marks the 47th WorldSkills Olympics, which is a global movement bringing together young professionals from across the world through competition-based training, assessment and benchmarking.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This year\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"the 47th WorldSkills Olympics\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"a global movement\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"young professionals\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1957}, {\"